      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Spokane will soon have two more\nunions added to it's already long list,\nthe bookkeepers and cement workers\nhaving applied for charters from the\nAmerican Federation of Labor. AS\nsoon as the charters arrive the unions\nwill be formed by Organizer Young,\nwho has been in the city for some\ntime in the interests of the American\nFederation of Labor."
